Title: Degeneracy of Landau levels and quantum group sl q (2)  
Author: Guang-Hong Chen Le-Man Kuang yz and Mo-Lin Ge 
Date: December 16, 1997  
Address: Hunan Normal University, Hunan 410006, P.R.China  
Affiliation: yTheoretical Physics Division, Nankai Institute of Mathematics, Tianjin 300071, P.R.China zDepartment of Physics,  
Abstract: We show that there is a kind of quantum group symmetry sl q (2) in the usual Landau problem and it is this quantum group symmetry that governs the degeneracy of Landau levels. Especially, we discuss the relationship between the cyclic representation of the quantum group and the degeneracy of Landau levels. PACS number(s): 03.65.Fd, 02.20.+b 
